description:
For more than a year she has kept us waiting and stewing, Germany’s Queen of Rubber, until we could finally shoot a new film with her. And it was worth the wait, even prettier than ever before, even meaner than you know her and even more sadistic than you might think, a completely defenseless rubber doll strapped to the “Boomer” experiences her Rubbber Goddess in absolute top form! NS, electricity, anal there is the full program, but unfortunately no orgasm… grin

(Part 1 of 2)
title: Lady Ashley - "Rubber Drift"
